T01D1143:104a-1: pa da sya aashta ka sto tram /
T01D1143:104a-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1143:104a-5: zla rgyas zhal 'dra khyu mchog 'dra ba'i spyan //
T01D1143:104a-6: seng ge'i sgra 'dra glang po'i stobs 'dra zhing //
T01D1143:104a-7: ri dbang rgyal brtan rgya mtsho 'dra ba'i thugs //
T01D1143:104a-8: lha dbang bla ma'i thugs dbang phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1143:104a-9: spyan gsum spyan legs pad+ma ltar yangs spyan //
T01D1143:104a-10: gnod sbyin klu yi mi 'dras gzigs mdzad cing //
T01D1143:104a-11: thar pa thob mdzad spyan ni dkyus ring ba //
T01D1143:104a-12: spyan stong gzigs pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1143:104a-13: lha mchog du ma'i yan lag mchog gis btud //
T01D1143:104a-14: btso ma'i gser ltar 'bar sku mchod 'os sku //
T01D1143:104a-15: mtshan bzangs mdzes pas rnam par brgyan pa'i sku //
T01D1143:104a-16: bde gshegs de la spyi bos phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1143:104a-17: blo gros rgyas shing gser ltar dri ma med //
T01D1143:104a-18: blo gros grags shing mkhas pa'i blo dang ldan //
T01D1143:104b-0: sangs rgyas mkha' ltar dri med spyan @104b mnga' ba //
T01D1143:104b-1: dpa' bo mi g-yo blo mnga' de la 'dud //
T01D1143:104b-2: smra ba'i mchog gyur snyan pa'i don gsung pa //
T01D1143:104b-3: yang dag don gsung 'dul ba'i don gsung zhing //
T01D1143:104b-4: smra ba'i dbang phyug rgol bas mi bskyod gsung //
T01D1143:104b-5: bden bzhi gsung ba'i rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1143:104b-6: gzhan du mi 'dul 'dul ba'i don du 'dul //
T01D1143:104b-7: nyon mongs spong sogs rnams par dag pas 'dul //
T01D1143:104b-8: thub pa tshul spyod chen pos legs par mdzad //
T01D1143:104b-9: snyoms shing mdzes pa'i tshems ldan mgon la 'dud //
T01D1143:104b-10: bsod nams dpag med bsags pas sku mdzes la //
T01D1143:104b-12: gser sbyangs btso ma lta bur dri med sku //
T01D1143:104b-13: srid las grol sku rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1143:104b-14: 'khor los zhabs gnas mchog gi mtshan ldan zhabs //
T01D1143:104b-15: lha dbang spyi bos legs pa rab tu btud pa'i zhabs //
T01D1143:104b-16: zhabs sor dra bas legs brgyan mdzes pa'i zhabs//
T01D1143:104b-17: dpal be'u g-yung drung gis mtshan zhabs la 'dud //
